# CogniAgent

**A cognitive AI Agent framework — agents with self-awareness, memory, and evolution.**

[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](LICENSE)
[![Python 3.11+](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.11+-blue.svg)](pyproject.toml)
[![Tests](https://img.shields.io/badge/tests-103%20passed-brightgreen.svg)](#)

```python
from cogni_agent import AgentRuntime
from cogni_agent.tools import WebSearch, Calculator, ComputerScreenshot

# 创建带自我认知的 Agent
agent = await AgentRuntime.create(
    name="小悟",
    role="数据分析师",
    personality=["严谨", "友善"],
    tools=[WebSearch(), Calculator(), ComputerScreenshot()],
)

# 分配任务 — Agent 会自主推理、调用工具、反思进化
result = await agent.run("搜索最近的 AI 新闻趋势")
```

---

## 🌟 核心理念

大多数 Agent 框架是**流程编排器**（定义 DAG、串接工具）。CogniAgent 完全不同：

| 维度 | 竞品 | **CogniAgent** |
|---|---|---|
| 🧠 **核心** | 流程编排 (DAG/Pipeline) | **认知引擎 (Brain)** |
| 👤 **自我认知** | ❌ 无 | ✅ **Identity Profile / Capability Map / 关系模型** |
| 🔄 **自动进化** | ❌ 每次从零开始 | ✅ **反思→学习→适应→巩固 进化飞轮** |
| 💾 **记忆系统** | 单层对话历史 | ✅ **工作/语义/情景/程序 四层架构** |
| 🔧 **工具调用** | 固定流程节点 | ✅ **21个工具，Agent 自主决策** |
| 🤖 **电脑控制** | ❌ 仅特定产品 | ✅ **截图/鼠标/键盘/窗口/Shell 跨平台** |
| 🌐 **依赖** | 必须 API Key | ✅ **DuckDuckGo 搜索 + 本地嵌入 零 Key 可用** |

---

## 📦 安装

```bash
pip install cogni-agent

# 或从源码安装
git clone https://github.com/cogni-agent/cogni-agent
cd cogni-agent
pip install -e .
```

### 可选依赖

```bash
pip install 'cogni-agent[web]'   # Web Console 可视化调试台
pip install 'cogni-agent[gui]'   # 鼠标/键盘图形化控制
pip install 'cogni-agent[all]'   # 全部功能
```

---

## 🚀 快速开始

### 1. 创建 Agent

```python
from cogni_agent import AgentRuntime

agent = await AgentRuntime.create(
    name="小悟",
    role="数据分析助手",
    personality=["严谨", "友善", "善于洞察"],
    values=["数据驱动决策"],
    model="gpt-4o",
)
```

### 2. 分配任务

```python
result = await agent.run("帮我分析一下当前 AI Agent 框架的市场格局")
print(result)
```

### 3. 查看自我认知

```python
# 能力置信度地图
print(agent.get_capability_map())
# → [{"name": "chat", "confidence": 0.7}, ...]

# 进化历史
print(agent.get_evolution_history())
# → [{"type": "insight", "description": "..."}, ...]

# 完整自我认知报告
print(agent.get_self_summary())
```

---

## 🛠️ 21 个内置工具

| 类别 | 工具 | 平台 | 需 API Key |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Web** | `web_search` | 🍎🐧 | ❌ |
| **Web** | `web_fetch` | 🍎🐧 | ❌ |
| **文件** | `file_read` / `file_write` / `file_list` | 🍎🐧 | ❌ |
| **计算** | `calculator` | 🍎🐧 | ❌ |
| **编程** | `python_repl` (沙箱) | 🍎🐧 | ❌ |
| **电脑** | `computer_screenshot` | 🍎🐧 | ❌ |
| **电脑** | `computer_mouse_move` / `computer_mouse_click` / `computer_mouse_scroll` | 🍎🐧 | ❌ |
| **电脑** | `computer_type` / `computer_hotkey` / `computer_press` | 🍎🐧 | ❌ |
| **电脑** | `computer_screen_info` / `computer_list_windows` / `computer_focus_window` | 🍎🐧 | ❌ |
| **电脑** | `computer_open` / `computer_terminal` | 🍎🐧 | ❌ |
| **脚本** | `computer_shell` (bash) | 🍎🐧 | ❌ |
| **脚本** | `computer_applescript` | 🍎 | ❌ |

```python
from cogni_agent import AgentRuntime
from cogni_agent.tools import WebSearch, Calculator, PythonREPL, ComputerScreenshot

agent = await AgentRuntime.create(
    name="全能助手",
    tools=[WebSearch(), Calculator(), PythonREPL(), ComputerScreenshot()],
)
```

